title: Ander Herrera has female United fan lookalike (photos)
text:
Tweet 
Manchester United midfielder Ander Herrera has a had a fine run of form lately. Man of the Match material, his heroism at Everton, and much more have made Herrera a player that Louis van Gaal can’t afford not to select lately. The name Ander Herrera trends on social media whenever he does something notable on the pitch, but his name went viral for a totally different reason this week. It turns out he had a Manchester United supporter lookalike, who’s female! Take a look. Her sister even Tweeted the picture to Herrera. @AnderHerrera seriously mate are you and my sister related or something?? pic.twitter.com/JIR0JuwUgc
